<br>
Wherever you decide to fight him (both the ones mentioned work brt), try to make sure your MT is on the phone with someone, or two boxing another toon at the fight.  He'll be blind about 90% of the fight, and if not positioned correctly, getting blown all over the place, not holding aggro, etc.  <br>
<br>
Until Verant &quot;fixes&quot; blind to only remove the rendered image (possible with the new UI, since the windows are overlays instead of part of the rendered image), having someone tell the MT where he is/facing, or being able to watch from another toon's point of view, is pretty much the only way I can &quot;see&quot; to keeping positioning down reliably.  Even if you can keep in the corner, getting spun by a stun can really mess things up...<br>
